snippet.title: Strayed Lights - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming April 25th, 2023 - Wishlist now: https://linktr.ee/strayedlights

Strayed Lights is an atmospheric action-adventure game with fast-paced, rewarding combat scored by Austin Wintory.
